data.title: M-Sales Credit
data.description: M-Sales Credit is a collaboration tool that organizes projects into boards. In one glance, M-Sales Credit tells you what's being worked on, who's working on what, and where something is in a process. Imagine a white board, filled with lists of sticky notes, with each note as a task for you and your team. This system is specifically for monitoring sales surveys.
